"Revenge"
The following entry brought to you by Dave (IAMHOLTZ@oak.grove.iup.edu)
The first thing I wanted to do was put huge gashes in his arms and toss him in
to a pool of lemon juice. But I didn't know where I'd find all that lemon juice.
So then I thought it might be an interesting way of getting revenge if I cut
open his back, tie a bungy cord around his spine, toss him off a cliff, holding
the bungy cord, hoping that when the cord came back up all there would be was
bones. But that would probably get me sick and make me fall off the cliff. So
my last resort was ... well let me tell you what he did to me first...
I thought it would be neat to yell across the classroom how much of a snob he
was, and he really was, is. He wasn't pleased. After class, he got in my face,
like right in my face, practically trying to get a piece. I had notions about
him at this point. he wanted to get his two cents in. He said I wouldn't
amount to anything. Called him a homosexual that day, not that there's
anything wrong with that, not at all. But well, it seemed right. And I know
right from wrong, after all I'm amoral. I like eating dead cow too, but that
doesn't piss me off like he does. So he was all mad, and then he striked me
about the face with the back of his hand. I think they call that a back hand.
Makes sense, it's accurate, precise and all that. I was sucking on a  breath
mint hardcore. He striked me he did. And the mint like flew outta my mouth.
That mint was given to me by this philosopher guy so it had sentimental
value. So then he called me a Jewish, nigger loving, white trash faggot but
that's not what pissed me off. It was the breath mint. I love breath mints,
not that there's anything wrong with that. And I like dead cows so i think
I'll just write big "X's" on my hands.  So what did I finally decide to do to
him? What evil maniacal thing could I possibly think of? What would get him
right where it counts? What absolutely impulsive diabolical act of revenge
could I present him with? Well I'll tell you. You wanna know what I said?
What great thing did I do to get back at his utterly violent action towards me?
Heh. I said, " you know what pal? You rock!"

